overview: Friends Rashaun and Damon are talented basketball players from the same inner-city neighborhood. Both are NBA hopefuls; but Rashaun is the more coveted pick among college recruitment scouts. The snag… Rashaun’s passion isn't basketball, instead, he desires to be a sculptor. A broken promise becomes a broken dream. Although Rashaun's journey to follow his passion is plagued with systemic disadvantages he is determined to not be defeated by his internal head noise.
title: HeadNoise
